<paragraph blockId="20.[160,1156,627,757]" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,268,627,653]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ahmad M &amp; Jairajpuri MS" box="[285,611,628,653]" pageId="20" pageNumber="331" pagination="233 - 246" refId="ref17900" refString="Ahmad M, Jairajpuri MS. 1982. Three new and two known species of dorylaim nematodes with proposal of Acephalodorylaimus n. gen. Nematologica. 28 (2): 233 - 246. doi: 10.1163 / 187529282 X 00088." type="journal article" year="1982">Ahmad and Jairajpuri (1982)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ahmad and Jairajpuri" authorityYear="1982" box="[740,1038,628,653]" class="Adenophorea" family="Leptonchidae" genus="Dorylaimoides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Dorylaimida" pageId="20" pageNumber="331" phylum="Nematoda" rank="species" species="malabaricus">
<emphasis box="[740,1038,628,653]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">Dorylaimoides malabaricus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on 
<specimenCount box="[160,294,663,688]" pageId="20" pageNumber="331" type="female">one female</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount box="[361,501,663,688]" pageId="20" pageNumber="331" type="male">three males</specimenCount>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[579,652,663,688]" country="India" name="Kerala" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">Kerala</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[667,726,663,688]" name="India" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">India</collectingCountry>
. The morphometrics of the present population conform well with the 
<typeStatus box="[563,613,697,722]" pageId="20" pageNumber="331">type</typeStatus>
population except in having a slightly shorter odontostyle (8.0–9.0 vs 11 μm).
</paragraph>
